Mustex and Stallex arrive.

Mustex: Real smooth Mustex.  A bots in trouble and you leave the 
technician behind.  Mustex looks at the bot and begins slappping wires 
together.

Mustex:  Stallex this is an Autobot capsule. We've gone back in time.

Mustex desperately trys to get the life support systems back up.  He 
knows this things only chance is either to have his or Stallex's DNA 
scanners implanted (remember all bots have them built in since "Beast 
Machines") or to live long enough to get back.  The only major peice 
of machinery around is the Shuttle.  Then he remembers the 
hover-cycles.

Mustex:  STALLEX!  GET ONE OF THOSE CYCLES OVER HERE PRONTO!
